OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters loses battle
OL,4,Cwith cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FThe frontman of rock band The Alarm
OL,7,Fhas died at the age of 66.
OL,9,FMike Peters had been fighting an
OL,10,Faggressive form of blood cancer for 30
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FIn September 2024, the musician had
OL,14,Fannounced he was in remission from
OL,15,Fchronic slow-growing lymphocytic
OL,16,Fleukaemia (CLL), a type of cancer of
OL,17,Fthe blood and bone marrow.
OL,19,FBut the Welsh music icon died on the
OL,20,Fevening of 28 April surrounded by his
OL,21,Ffamily.
