OL,3,C80s rock icon Mike Peters loses battle
OL,4,Cwith cancer at the age of 66
OL,6,FPeters, who has supported the likes of
OL,7,FU2 and Status Quo on tour, first rose
OL,8,Fto fame in the early 1980s with The
OL,9,FAlarm as anthems like '68 Guns' and
OL,10,F'Strength' gathering international
OL,11,Facclaim.
OL,13,FThe band's US tour was cancelled in
OL,14,F2024 due the musician's illness.
OL,16,FFive days before he was due to fly to
OL,17,FChicago for the 50-date tour, he
OL,18,Fnoticed that a lump in his neck had
OL,19,Fappeared overnight.
