OL,6,FDoctors quickly realised the star had
OL,7,Fdeveloped Richter's syndrome, where
OL,8,FCLL changes into a much more
OL,9,Faggressive lymphoma.
OL,11,FPeters leaves his wife Jules, 58, and
OL,12,Ftwo sons, Dylan, 20, and Evan, 18.
